item.title: Become a supporter
item.description: Autobotz is always looking forward to make new connections with great companies. If you want to support our team you can contact us directly using our contact us page. As an Autobotz sponsor we will proudly use your logo at our robots and projects. The Autobotz team is also highly qualified to offer workshops using your products either in big events like the Maker Fair or FINIT, or inside the UFMG Engineering School.
